  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <lg xml:id="TolC256">
          <l>pirinilai viṉaivē yetirmaṟai yoḻiyicai</l>
          <l>terinilaik kiḷavi ciṟappoṭu tokaii</l>
          <l>yirumūṉ ṟeṉpa vōkā rammē.</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/160/mode/1up">160</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/161/mode/1up">161</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ic cūttiram eṉṉutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, mēl tattaṅ kuṟippiṟ poruḷceykuvaṉa uṇarttiṉār; iṉi maṟṟu eṉpatōr iṭaiccol viṉaimāṟṟum acainilaiyumāy varum eṉpatu uṇarttukiṉṟār.
      </p>
      <p>varalāṟu:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘iḵtu uṇ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṟāṟku,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Ilam-cit2">
        <l>‘maṟṟu uṇpal’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa, viṉaimāṟṟu āyiṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
yāvarōṭāyiṉuñ collāṭāniṉṟu
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Ilam-cit3">
        <l>‘maṟṟōmaṟṟu’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṉum iṭaiyē; aḵtu acainilaik kaṭṭurai. (14)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n212/mode/1up">209</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i - ḷ. pirinilaipporuṭṭālatu mutalāka okāram aṟuvakaippaṭum. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u - m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Cena-cit1">
        <l>‘yāṉō tēṟēṉavar poyvaḻaṅkalarē’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu tēṟuvār piṟariṟpirittaliṟ pirinilaiyeccamāyiṟṟu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Cena-cit2">
        <l>cāttaṉuṇṭāṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu viṉāvōkāram.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Cena-cit3">
        <l>yāṉō koḷvēṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu, koḷḷēṉṉeṉṉu metirmaṟai kuṟittu niṟṟaliṉ, etirmaṟaiyōkāramām.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Cena-cit4">
        <l>koḷakō koṇṭāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu, koṇṭuyyappōyiṉāṉallaṉ eṉpatu mutalāya oḻiyicai nōkki niṟṟaliṉ, oḻiyicaiyōkāram.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Cena-cit5">
        <l>tirumakaḷōvallaḷ aramakaḷōvallaḷ ivaḷ yār</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṟavaḻit teritaṟkaṇ varutaliṟṟerinilaiyōkāram.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Cena-cit6">
        <l>ōoperiyaṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu perumaimikutiyuṇarttaliṟ ciṟappōkāram. (8)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/289/mode/1up">289</ref>.</p>
      <p>
‘o’ eṉṉu miṭaic colliṉ poruḷ
      </p>
      <lg>
        <l>pirinilai viṉaivē yetirmaṟai yoḻiyicai</l>
        <l>terinilaik kiḷavi ciṟappoṭu tokaii</l>
        <l>yirumūṉ ṟeṉpa vōkā rammē.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
ituvumatu.
      </p>
      <p>
(i-ḷ) pirinilai viṉāvē yetirmaṟai yoḻi yicai terinilaik kiḷavi ciṟappoṭu tokaii yirumūṉṟeṉpa vōkārammē - pirinilaip poruṇmai viṉāp poruṇmai, etirmaṟaip poruṇmai, eñci niṉṟa coṟ poruṇmai ārāyum nilaimaiyai yuṭaiya poruṇmai eṉkiṉṟa vivaṟṟai mikutip poruṇmaiyōṭē tokut tōkārap poruṇmai yāṟeṉṟu kūṟuvarāciriya reṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n177/mode/1up">170</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n178/mode/1up">171</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i-ḷ: ― pirinilai mutalāka ōtappaṭṭa āṟiṭamum eṉṟu colluvār: ōkāramākiya iṭaiccol poruḷ uṇarttu miṭam. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u-m: ― pirinilaiyāvatu piṟaporuḷiṉiṉṟum pirittamai tōṉṟavaruvatu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Tey-cit1">
        <l>kāṉaṅ kāreṉak kūṟiṉum,</l>
        <l>yāṉō tēṟeṉavar poyvaḻaṅ kalarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Tey-cit2">
        <l>avarō vārār</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉavarum. ellārum tēṟiṉum yāṉ tēṟēṉ, ellārum variṉum avar vārār eṉap pirinilaip poruṇmai tōṉṟiyavāṟu kaṇṭukoḷka. viṉā eṉpatu viṉāvutaṟ poruṇmēlvarum.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Tey-cit3">
        <l>atuvō?</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Tey-cit4">
        <l>uṇṭāyō?</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉavarum. etirmaṟaiyāvatu taṉaṉāṟ collappaṭṭa poruḷiṉ māṟupaṭṭu varuvatu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Tey-cit5">
        <l>uṇṇēṉō,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Tey-cit6">
        <l>vārēṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṟavaḻi uṇpal, varuval eṉṉum poruḷ paṭṭaṉa. oḻiyicaiyāvatu taṉṉāṟcollappaṭṭa poruḷaṉṟi maṟṟoru poruḷuṅ koḷḷa niṟpatu. ceykaiyō cey tāṉ eṉṟavaḻip, piṉpum ivvāṟu ceytilaṉ eṉṉum poruḷuṅ kuṟittu niṉṟavāṟu kaṇṭukoḷka. terinilai eṉpatu oruporuḷai ārāyum nilaimaikkaṇ varuvatu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Tey-cit7">
        <l>tirumakaḷō allaḷ, (ara)makaḷō vallaḷ, ivaḷ yār ākum</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉavarum. 
      </p>
      <p>
ciṟappoṉpatu poruḷi.................. kuṟittu niṟkum,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Tey-cit8">
        <l>kāṉaka nāṭaṉai nīyōo porum</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉavarum. aḵtēl eḻuttati kārattu ōkāravīṟṟuḷ aiyameṉṟum ōr ōkāram ōtiṉārāleṉiṉ, atu terinilaikkaṇ aṭaṅkum eṉpatu umoṉṟu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Tey-cit9">
        <l>vantatu kaṇṭu vārātatu muṭittal</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpataṉāl, āṇṭu māṟu koḷ eccamum, viṉāvum, aiyamum eṉa ōtappaṭṭavaṟṟuḷ vārātatuṅ koḷḷappaṭum. oruvaṉō, oruttiyō tōṉṟu kiṉṟār eṉavarum.
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Kallāṭaṉār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Cuntaramūrtti</persName> 1964, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/TVG27Tolkappiyam/page/199/mode/1up">199</ref>.</p>
      <p>
eṉ - eṉiṉ, ituvum atu.
      </p>
      <p>
(i - ḷ.) pirinilaipporuṇmai, viṉāpporuṇmai, etirmaṟaip poruṇmai, oḻiyicaip poruṇmai, terinilaip poruṇmai eṉa ivaṟṟaic ciṟappup poruṇmaiyōṭu tokuttu āṟu eṉṟu collup āciriyar ōkārattup poruṇmai, (e - ṟu.)
      </p>
      <p>
(e - ṭu.) pirinilai -
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Kal-cit1">
        <l>avaṉō tōṇṭāṉ eṉpatu.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
iḵtu ippōtu viṉāvāy naṭakkiṉṟateṉa uṇarka.
      </p>
      <p>
iṉi viṉā -
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Kal-cit2">
        <l>avaṉō allaṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
iṉi etirmaṟai -
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Kal-cit3">
        <l>yāṉōkoḷvēṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu.
      </p>
      <p>
iṉi oḻiyicai -
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Kal-cit4">
        <l>koḷalō koṇṭāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu.
      </p>
      <p>
iṉi terinilai -
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Kal-cit5">
        <l>naṉṟōvaṉṟu titōvaṉṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu.
      </p>
      <p>
iṉi ciṟappu -
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC256-Kal-cit6">
        <l>ōṭuparitu</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu. (8)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
